metadata.name: Merry-go-round
metadata.description:
The merry-go-round goes round and round. 
Feeling like a child again, I play and reminisce.

When I took this picture, It reminded me of the past.
And now I see this picture, It reminds me of that time.
Merry-go-round brings me back to the old days.
